title: Top 10 Films: July 3-5, 2015
text:
July 5 at 5:27 PM Top 10 Films “Jurassic World” just barely came out on top over the holiday weekend. The number of weeks open for each film is in parentheses.
Weekend Total in millions of dollars 1.  Jurassic World (4) 30.9 558.1 2.  Inside Out (3) 30.1 246.2 3.  Terminator: Genisys (1) 28.7 44.2 4.  Magic Mike XXL (1) 11.6 26.7 5.  Ted 2 (2) 11.0 58.3 6.  Max (2) 6.6 25.3 7.  Spy (5) 5.5 97.9 8.  San Andreas (6) 3.0 147.4 9.  Me and Earl and the Dying Girl (4) 1.3 4.0 10.  Dope (3) 1.1 14.1 Source: www.boxofficemojo.com
